<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-TW">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title><%= serviceName %> - 服務文檔</title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #FF6B35 0%, #F7931E 100%);
            min-height: 100vh;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        .header {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.95);
            border-radius: 15px;
            padding: 30px;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            text-align: center;
        }

        .header h1 {
            color: #D84315;
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            font-weight: 700;
        }

        .header .service-icon {
            font-size: 4rem;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }

        .version-badge {
            display: inline-block;
            background: linear-gradient(45deg, #FF6B35, #F7931E);
            color: white;
            padding: 5px 15px;
            border-radius: 20px;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            margin-top: 10px;
        }

        .description {
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            color: #555;
            margin: 15px 0;
        }

        .features-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
            gap: 25px;
            margin-bottom: 40px;
        }

        .feature-card {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.95);
            border-radius: 15px;
            padding: 25px;
            box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            transition: transform 0.3s ease;
            border-left: 5px solid #FF6B35;
        }

        .feature-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-5px);
            box-shadow: 0 15px 35px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);
        }

        .feature-header {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }

        .feature-icon {
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            margin-right: 10px;
            color: #FF6B35;
        }

        .feature-title {
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #D84315;
        }

        .feature-description {
            color: #666;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }

        .endpoint-list {
            background: #f5f5f5;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 15px;
        }

        .endpoint-item {
            background: white;
            padding: 8px 12px;
            margin: 5px 0;
            border-radius: 5px;
            font-family: 'Courier New', monospace;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            border-left: 3px solid #FF6B35;
        }

        .architecture-section {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.95);
            border-radius: 15px;
            padding: 30px;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        .architecture-title {
            color: #D84315;
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .architecture-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr));
            gap: 20px;
        }

        .architecture-item {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px;
            background: #f8f9fa;
            border-radius: 10px;
            border: 2px solid #ffccbc;
        }

        .architecture-item h4 {
            color: #D84315;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .examples-section {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.95);
            border-radius: 15px;
            padding: 30px;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        .example-card {
            background: #f8f9fa;
            border-radius: 10px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            border-left: 4px solid #FF6B35;
        }

        .example-title {
            color: #D84315;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .step-list {
            list-style: none;
            padding: 0;
        }

        .step-item {
            background: white;
            margin: 5px 0;
            padding: 10px 15px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            border-left: 3px solid #8BC34A;
        }

        .navigation {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 20px;
            margin-top: 30px;
        }

        .nav-btn {
            display: inline-block;
            background: linear-gradient(45deg, #FF6B35, #F7931E);
            color: white;
            padding: 12px 25px;
            border-radius: 25px;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: 600;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(255, 107, 53, 0.3);
        }

        .nav-btn:hover {
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: 0 6px 20px rgba(255, 107, 53, 0.4);
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
        }

        .footer {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.95);
            border-radius: 15px;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            margin-top: 30px;
        }

        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .header h1 {
                font-size: 2rem;
            }
            
            .features-grid {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
            }
            
            .navigation {
                flex-direction: column;
                align-items: center;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <!-- Header -->
        <div class="header">
            <div class="service-icon">🔑</div>
            <h1><%= serviceName %></h1>
            <div class="description"><%= description %></div>
            <div class="version-badge">版本 <%= version %></div>
        </div>

        <!-- Core Features -->
        <div class="features-grid">
            <!-- JWT Authentication -->
            <div class="feature-card">
                <div class="feature-header">
                    <span class="feature-icon">🔐</span>
                    <span class="feature-title">JWT 身份驗證</span>
                </div>
                <div class="feature-description">
                    基於 JSON Web Token 的現代身份驗證系統，提供安全可靠的使用者認證
                </div>
                <div class="endpoint-list">
                    <div class="endpoint-item">POST /auth/login - 使用者登入</div>
                    <div class="endpoint-item">POST /auth/logout - 使用者登出</div>
                    <div class="endpoint-item">POST /auth/refresh - 刷新 Token</div>
                    <div class="endpoint-item">GET /auth/me - 獲取當前使用者</div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Token Management -->
            <div class="feature-card">
                <div class="feature-header">
                    <span class="feature-icon">🎫</span>
                    <span class="feature-title">Token 管理</span>
                </div>
                <div class="feature-description">
                    完整的 Token 生命週期管理，包括生成、驗證、刷新和撤銷機制
                </div>
                <div class="endpoint-list">
                    <div class="endpoint-item">POST /tokens/generate - 生成新 Token</div>
                    <div class="endpoint-item">POST /tokens/validate - 驗證 Token</div>
                    <div class="endpoint-item">POST /tokens/revoke - 撤銷 Token</div>
                    <div class="endpoint-item">GET /tokens/status - Token 狀態查詢</div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Password Security -->
            <div class="feature-card">
                <div class="feature-header">
                    <span class="feature-icon">🛡️</span>
                    <span class="feature-title">密碼安全</span>
                </div>
                <div class="feature-description">
                    強化的密碼安全機制，包括雜湊加密、密碼策略和重設功能
                </div>
                <div class="endpoint-list">
                    <div class="endpoint-item">POST /auth/password/hash - 密碼雜湊</div>
                    <div class="endpoint-item">POST /auth/password/verify - 密碼驗證</div>
                    <div class="endpoint-item">POST /auth/password/reset - 密碼重設</div>
                    <div class="endpoint-item">GET /auth/password/policy - 密碼政策</div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Session Management -->
            <div class="feature-card">
                <div class="feature-header">
                    <span class="feature-icon">⏰</span>
                    <span class="feature-title">會話管理</span>
                </div>
                <div class="feature-description">
                    靈活的會話管理系統，支援多裝置登入、會話追蹤和過期處理
                </div>
                <div class="endpoint-list">
                    <div class="endpoint-item">GET /sessions - 獲取使用者會話</div>
                    <div class="endpoint-item">DELETE /sessions/:id - 終止特定會話</div>
                    <div class="endpoint-item">DELETE /sessions/all - 終止所有會話</div>
                    <div class="endpoint-item">GET /sessions/active - 活躍會話統計</div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Architecture -->
        <div class="architecture-section">
            <h2 class="architecture-title">🏗️ 服務架構</h2>
            <div class="architecture-grid">
                <div class="architecture-item">
                    <h4>🗄️ 資料庫</h4>
                    <p>MySQL</p>
                    <small>使用者與會話資料</small>
                </div>
                <div class="architecture-item">
                    <h4>⚡ 快取</h4>
                    <p>Redis</p>
                    <small>Token 快取與黑名單</small>
                </div>
                <div class="architecture-item">
                    <h4>🔗 通訊</h4>
                    <p>gRPC + HTTP</p>
                    <small>高效能認證服務</small>
                </div>
                <div class="architecture-item">
                    <h4>🔐 加密</h4>
                    <p>bcrypt + JWT</p>
                    <small>密碼與 Token 安全</small>
                </div>
                <div class="architecture-item">
                    <h4>🔍 服務發現</h4>
                    <p>Consul</p>
                    <small>認證服務註冊</small>
                </div>
                <div class="architecture-item">
                    <h4>📋 架構模式</h4>
                    <p>CQRS</p>
                    <small>命令查詢責任分離</small>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Usage Examples -->
        <div class="examples-section">
            <h2 class="architecture-title">💡 使用範例</h2>
            
            <div class="example-card">
                <div class="example-title">🔑 使用者登入認證流程</div>
                <ol class="step-list">
                    <li class="step-item">使用者提交登入資訊：POST /auth/login</li>
                    <li class="step-item">系統驗證密碼：bcrypt 雜湊比對</li>
                    <li class="step-item">生成 JWT Token：包含使用者資訊</li>
                    <li class="step-item">建立會話記錄：Redis 快取會話狀態</li>
                    <li class="step-item">回傳認證結果：Token 和使用者資料</li>
                </ol>
            </div>

            <div class="example-card">
                <div class="example-title">🛡️ Token 驗證與授權流程</div>
                <ol class="step-list">
                    <li class="step-item">接收 API 請求：Bearer Token 認證</li>
                    <li class="step-item">驗證 Token 有效性：POST /tokens/validate</li>
                    <li class="step-item">檢查黑名單狀態：Redis 快速查詢</li>
                    <li class="step-item">解析使用者權限：與 RBAC 服務整合</li>
                    <li class="step-item">授權請求處理：允許或拒絕存取</li>
                </ol>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Navigation -->
        <div class="navigation">
            <a href="/api/docs/auth/typedoc" class="nav-btn">
                🔧 查看技術文檔 (TypeDoc)
            </a>
            <a href="/api/docs" class="nav-btn">
                🏠 返回文檔中心
            </a>
            <a href="/api/health" class="nav-btn">
                ❤️ 服務健康檢查
            </a>
        </div>

        <!-- Footer -->
        <div class="footer">
            <p>🕒 最後更新：<%= new Date(lastUpdated).toLocaleString('zh-TW') %></p>
            <p>🏗️ AIOT Development Team | 身份驗證與授權微服務</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>